-- BP Gulf Oil Spill Discussions Continue, U.S. Official Says
-- B y   S e t h   S t e r n
-- 2012-03-05T16:51:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-05/bp-gulf-oil-spill-discussions-continue-u-s-official-says.html
Discussions between the U.S. Justice
Department and companies involved in the 2010 Gulf of Mexico oil
spill are continuing after a $7.8 billion agreement between  BP
Plc (BP/)  and businesses and individuals harmed by the spill,
Assistant Attorney General  Tony West  said today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Seth Stern in  Washington  at 
